Class OrgDetailsItemHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • de.tum.in.tumcampus.adapters.OrgDetailsItemHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class OrgDetailsItemHandler
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    Class that handles an OrgDetailsObject and SAX-Parses the XML containing such Objects. The parsed Object has no child Objects (but can be implemented also with child Objects)
